products.description: Crafted by the legendary Wagner family, this wine showcases the signature Caymus style of richness and depth. It is approachable yet complex, bursting with flavors of lush dark berries, cocoa, and sweet vanilla. The wine’s velvety tannins contribute to a smooth, incredibly satisfying finish.

Instantly recognizable, this world-famous Champagne is a benchmark for its consistent quality and full-bodied style. It delivers a perfect balance of strength and silkiness, with aromatic intensity and notes of pear, lemon, and toasted brioche, culminating in a fresh, powerful finish.

Hailing from the prestigious Napa Valley, this wine embodies a perfect balance of power and elegance. It presents a deep bouquet of black cherry and cassis, seamlessly integrated with notes of rich cocoa and clove, all framed by polished tannins that lead to a smooth, lingering close.

From one of Napa Valley's most historic and revered wineries in the Rutherford AVA, this Cabernet is both classic and timeless. Look for signature notes of dark black cherry and cassis, elegantly layered with hints of violet and sweet oak spice, leading to a refined and velvety finish.

products.fullName: Louis M Martini Napa Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: From an iconic producer that helped define Napa Cabernet Sauvignon, this wine is a benchmark of quality and character. It opens with aromas of ripe blackberry and black cherry, followed by complex notes of baking spices and toasted oak. A full-bodied structure ensures a powerful, lasting impression.

products.fullName: Force & Grace Cabernet Sauvignon Paso 750 Ml
products.description: An expressive Cabernet from the sun-drenched vineyards of Paso Robles, a region celebrated for its bold wines. This bottle reveals intense aromas of dark cherry and ripe plum, complemented by savory notes of spice and leather, culminating in a full-bodied and satisfyingly robust finish.

products.fullName: Force & Grace Cabernet Sauvignon Paso 750 Ml
products.description: From the warm climate of Paso Robles, this Cabernet Sauvignon is bold and full-bodied. It delivers concentrated dark fruit flavors of blackcurrant, ripe plum, and boysenberry, layered with notes of dark chocolate, espresso, and toasted oak. Firm tannins provide a structured, lingering finish.

A distinguished Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon, this wine offers elegance and power. It features a complex bouquet of ripe blackberry, cassis, and plum, interwoven with nuances of cedar, graphite, and baking spices. Well-integrated tannins and balanced acidity lead to a long, polished finish.

A historic Napa Valley producer, Beaulieu Vineyard delivers a classic Cabernet Sauvignon with depth and structure. This wine presents ripe flavors of blackberry, cassis, and dark plum, framed by hints of mocha, vanilla, and savory herbs. Polished tannins contribute to its rich texture and long finish.

products.fullName: Louis M Martini Napa Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: A benchmark for Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon, this wine is known for its balance and complexity. It delivers concentrated notes of black cherry, blackberry, and cassis, complemented by hints of cedar, licorice, and dried herbs. Firm, well-integrated tannins give it a structured and lengthy finish.

Famed for its signature opulent style, this California Cabernet Sauvignon is rich and textural. It offers pronounced flavors of ripe blackberry, cassis, and cocoa, with layers of vanilla and licorice. Its plush, velvety tannins and a hint of residual sweetness create a uniquely smooth, approachable profile.

An iconic Champagne, this Brut is defined by the dominance of Pinot Noir in its blend. It presents a perfect balance of power and finesse, with notes of yellow apple, ripe pear, and citrus. Its signature toasty, brioche-like complexity from aging leads to a crisp, persistent finish with fine bubbles.

A classic and vivacious Brut Champagne from one of the most esteemed houses in Reims, France. It delights the senses with a lively bouquet of crisp green apple, pear, and bright citrus zest. Subtle notes of toasted brioche and almond add complexity to its fine, persistent effervescence.

Crafted from grapes grown on the rugged, volcanic slopes of Mount Veeder in Napa Valley, this wine offers remarkable depth and complexity. It unveils concentrated flavors of wild blackberry and raspberry, with sophisticated undertones of cedar, graphite, and savory herbs for a truly memorable tasting.

products.fullName: Orin Swift Palermo Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: A bold and artistic creation from winemaker Dave Phinney, Palermo is a quintessential Napa Valley Cabernet. Sourced from exceptional vineyards across the valley, it delivers an intense tapestry of ripe cassis, black cherry, and tobacco leaf, finishing with a powerful yet refined structure.

Staying true to the celebrated Rombauer style, this Napa Valley Cabernet is rich, opulent, and deeply satisfying. It greets the palate with a generous core of black cherry and cassis, seamlessly blended with notes of vanilla and sweet oak spices for a plush, memorable finish.

From the renowned Stags' Leap Winery in Napa Valley, this Chardonnay strikes a beautiful balance between vibrancy and richness. It displays enticing aromas of crisp green apple, pear, and bright citrus, enhanced by a subtle touch of creamy oak that lends texture and a long, refreshing finish.

products.fullName: The Calling Paso Robles Cabernet Sauvignon
products.description: A partnership between Jim Nantz and Peter Deutsch, this Paso Robles Cabernet Sauvignon is a testament to the region's prowess. It boasts a profile of lush, ripe dark fruit, beautifully accented by sweet vanilla bean and toasted oak notes, all coming together in a harmonious, full-bodied experience.

From the historic Stags' Leap Winery, this Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon is an elegant expression of its terroir. It offers a sophisticated palate of dark currant and blackberry, intertwined with intriguing notes of graphite and anise, all supported by firm tannins and a graceful structure.
products.location: Stags Leap District, Napa Valley, California

products.description: This iconic Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon expresses the character of its mountain-grown fruit. It exhibits deep flavors of black cherry, currant, and wild blackberry, accented by notes of cedar, tobacco, and anise. The wine's firm tannins and structured profile promise excellent ageability.

products.fullName: Orin Swift Palermo Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: A bold Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon, Palermo reflects the signature powerful style of Orin Swift. This wine is dense and concentrated, with layered flavors of cassis, black cherry, and raspberry, alongside notes of tobacco, dark chocolate, and graphite. Its immense structure and velvety tannins persist.

From a producer celebrated for its rich style, this Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon is full-bodied and fruit-forward. It presents lush flavors of black cherry, cassis, and ripe plum, integrated with notes of vanilla, sweet spice, and mocha from extensive oak aging. Supple tannins create a smooth finish.

Now known as Moët Impérial, this iconic Champagne is a symbol of celebration and elegance. It reveals a bright fruitiness with notes of green apple and citrus, complemented by nuances of minerals and white flowers. Hints of brioche and fresh nuts add a touch of maturity to the crisp finish.

Sourced from esteemed Napa Valley vineyards, this Cabernet Sauvignon delivers a classic profile of rich blackberry, ripe plum, and subtle cassis. Layers of mocha, toasted oak, and a hint of vanilla unfold on the palate, supported by well-structured tannins and a long, elegant finish.

A masterful blend sourced from a patchwork of prime Napa Valley vineyards, creating a wine of immense complexity and richness. Each sip unveils decadent layers of dark chocolate, ripe blackberry, and hazelnut, all woven together with supple tannins for a truly luxurious and textured mouthfeel.

products.fullName: Stags Leap Wine Cellars Chardonnay 750 Ml
products.description: The Karia Chardonnay from Stags Leap Wine Cellars is a vibrant and refreshing expression of Napa Valley. It shines with bright acidity and elegant notes of lemon curd, Asian pear, and white peach. A delicate touch of oak adds complexity and a hint of spice, leading to a crisp, clean finish.

From the high-elevation terroir of DAOU Mountain in Paso Robles' Adelaida District, this Reserve Cabernet is a powerhouse of flavor and elegance. It exhibits deep notes of blackberry, cassis, and graphite, accented by beautiful floral hints of violet, all framed by impeccably balanced tannins.

A Joe Wagner creation from the cool-climate Russian River Valley, this Pinot Noir is both luscious and layered. It offers a rich bouquet of ripe cherry and wild strawberry, complemented by earthy undertones and a hint of savory spice, all delivered with a smooth, velvety texture.

A beautifully crafted Pinot Noir that speaks to its boutique origins, showcasing the varietal's delicate yet complex nature. Expect a graceful dance of red fruit flavors like cherry and raspberry, with subtle hints of forest floor and spice, all leading to a silky, elegant, and persistent finish.

products.fullName: Belle Glos Dairyman Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: From a specific block within the Russian River Valley, the Dairyman vineyard Pinot Noir is a rich and compelling wine. It presents an aromatic explosion of ripe raspberry and cranberry, intricately woven with notes of baking spices and vanilla, all wrapped in a lush, velvety, and expansive palate.

A quintessential California sparkling wine from the acclaimed J Vineyards in Russian River Valley. This non-vintage brut is crisp and vibrant, showcasing a delightful blend of crisp apple, Asian pear, and toasted almond notes. Its fine, lively bubbles lead to a refreshing and celebratory finish.

products.fullName: Belle Glos Las Alturas Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: Sourced from the Santa Lucia Highlands, the Las Alturas vineyard yields a Pinot Noir of impressive depth and power. This wine is characterized by its deep ruby hue and intense flavors of dark cherry, wild blackberry, and a hint of clove, finishing with a rich, textural, and opulent mouthfeel.

products.fullName: Belle Glos Clark And Telephone Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: Hailing from the Clark and Telephone Vineyard in the Santa Maria Valley, this single-vineyard Pinot Noir is a bold expression of its terroir. It bursts with aromas and flavors of black cherry, wild raspberry, and a touch of sweet cocoa, all delivered with the signature Belle Glos opulent, rich style.

A versatile and elegant expression of California Pinot Noir, sourcing grapes from top regions like Monterey, Sonoma, and Santa Barbara. This wine features bright, inviting notes of red cherry and raspberry, accented by a subtle hint of cola and spice, all leading to a smooth, silky finish.

products.fullName: Stags Leap Wine Cellars Est Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: Representing the esteemed Stags Leap District, this estate Cabernet Sauvignon is a benchmark of elegance and power. It weaves together expressive notes of black cherry, raspberry, and dark plum with hints of cedar and spice, culminating in a beautifully balanced and age-worthy wine.
products.location: Stags Leap District, Napa Valley, California

products.description: A classic California Cabernet Sauvignon, this wine is known for its approachable and fruit-driven character. It showcases ripe flavors of blackberry, dark cherry, and cassis, complemented by notes of mocha, vanilla, and a touch of spice from oak aging. Smooth tannins provide structure for a soft, round finish.

A multi-AVA Napa Valley blend, this Cabernet Sauvignon is crafted in a rich, decadent style. It boasts intense aromas and flavors of blackberry pie, dark chocolate, and cassis, with undertones of toasted oak, vanilla, and baking spice. Its plush texture and velvety tannins create a full-bodied finish.

products.fullName: Stags Leap Wine Cellars Est Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: From the prestigious Stag's Leap District, this Cabernet Sauvignon is a model of power and elegance. It showcases a complex profile of blackcurrant, dark cherry, and violet, with underlying notes of cedar, graphite, and spice. Its fine-grained tannins and balanced acidity create a seamless, long finish.

A boutique expression of Pinot Noir, this wine typically showcases the finesse of its cool-climate sourcing, often from the Sonoma Coast. Expect elegant red fruit flavors of cherry and raspberry, complemented by earthy notes of forest floor, subtle spice, and well-integrated oak for a balanced, nuanced profile.

products.fullName: Belle Glos Las Alturas Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: From the Santa Lucia Highlands, this Pinot Noir is known for its deep color and powerful, fruit-driven style. It offers intense flavors of black cherry, ripe raspberry, and blackberry jam, layered with notes of vanilla, baking spice, and a hint of cocoa. A rich texture and smooth finish define this bold wine.

Reflecting its cool-climate origins, this multi-appellation Pinot Noir balances elegance and fruit. It features aromas and flavors of ripe red cherry, raspberry, and pomegranate, with subtle notes of cola, tea leaf, and toasted oak. A silky texture and bright acidity lead to a graceful, lingering finish.

This North Coast Chardonnay from Black Stallion Estate Winery is crafted for balance and complexity. It features elegant aromas of green apple, pear, and citrus zest, with subtle notes of toasted oak and spice. A bright acidity and creamy mid-palate lead to a crisp and refreshing finish.

Sourced from the cool Russian River Valley, this Reserve Chardonnay is both elegant and complex. It presents vibrant notes of crisp apple, pear, and lemon curd, beautifully integrated with hints of toasted brioche, vanilla, and spice from barrel fermentation. Bright acidity gives it a long, refined finish.

This Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc offers a bright and complex profile. It combines lively citrus notes of grapefruit and lime with riper flavors of melon and white peach. A hint of barrel fermentation adds a subtle creamy texture and complexity, balanced by crisp acidity for a refreshing, elegant finish.

Housed in a distinctive cut-glass bottle, this Italian Prosecco is fresh, crisp, and aromatic. Made from the Glera grape, it offers lively notes of green apple, ripe citrus, and white flowers. Fine, persistent bubbles and a clean, fruity finish make it a perfect celebratory or aperitif sparkling wine.

products.fullName: J Vineyards Multi Appelation Chardonnay 750 Ml
products.description: Sourcing fruit from California’s finest cool-climate vineyards, this J Vineyards Chardonnay is both bright and balanced. It delivers an appealing mix of tropical fruit, like pineapple and mango, with hints of crisp apple and a touch of vanilla from gentle oak aging for a layered, refreshing wine.

A showcase of California's sparkling wine prowess, the J California Cuvée is crisp, elegant, and perfectly balanced. It opens with notes of crisp apple, Asian pear, and a hint of citrus blossom. The palate is creamy and refined, with a lively effervescence and a sophisticated, lingering finish.

A vibrant and refreshing sparkling Rosé from one of California's top producers. This wine is bursting with aromas and flavors of fresh strawberry, ripe raspberry, and red cherry, with a hint of watermelon. Its bright acidity and crisp finish make it a perfect companion for a sunny afternoon.

A classic expression of California sparkling wine, Chandon Brut is consistently crisp, fresh, and complex. It features signature notes of apple, pear, and bright citrus, beautifully layered with hints of almond and caramel from aging. It’s a versatile and reliable choice for any festive occasion.

products.fullName: William Hill Cc Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: Reflecting the diverse terroir of California's Central Coast, this Pinot Noir is ripe and well-balanced. It features a pleasing core of black cherry and strawberry fruit, complemented by subtle notes of brown sugar and spice from oak aging, all culminating in a smooth and silky mouthfeel.

products.fullName: Talbott Kali Hart Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: From the celebrated Talbott estate in Monterey, the Kali Hart Pinot Noir is both luscious and refined. It displays enticing aromas of ripe cherry, cranberry, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is smooth and layered, with a rich texture and subtle notes of baking spice that lead to an elegant finish.

A vibrant and aromatic expression from Rombauer, this Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc is bursting with life. It features an exhilarating blend of grapefruit, passionfruit, and pineapple notes, with a hint of fresh lime. The palate is crisp and juicy, leading to a long, mouthwatering, and lively finish.

A stylish and modern Prosecco designed for effortless enjoyment and celebratory moments. This Italian sparkler is crisp and refreshing, showcasing classic notes of green apple, white peach, and a hint of floral blossom. Its lively effervescence and clean finish make it an instant crowd-pleaser.

From the windswept Santa Lucia Highlands, this Chardonnay is rich and expressive. It boasts a beautiful aromatic profile of tropical fruits, lemon cream pie, and a hint of vanilla. The palate is full-bodied and creamy, balanced by a bright acidity that gives it a lively, persistent finish.

Grown in the Santa Lucia Highlands, this Pinot Noir is a bold and concentrated expression of the varietal. It reveals deep flavors of black cherry, ripe raspberry, and a touch of earthiness, all supported by a firm structure and hints of spice from barrel aging, culminating in a long, powerful finish.

This North Coast Cabernet Sauvignon offers a crowd-pleasing, accessible style. It is characterized by bright flavors of red cherry, blackberry, and plum, with subtle undertones of vanilla and oak spice. With medium body and soft tannins, it provides a smooth and easy-drinking experience for any occasion.

From the Lodi appellation, this Cabernet Sauvignon lives up to its bold name. It is a full-bodied, fruit-driven wine bursting with flavors of ripe blackberry, cherry cola, and toasted vanilla. Hints of spice and a velvety texture from oak aging lead to a smooth, crowd-pleasing, and powerful finish.

This North Coast Cabernet Sauvignon is crafted to be both powerful and graceful. It delivers alluring aromas and flavors of black cherry, cassis, and ripe plum, layered with complex notes of vanilla, espresso, and spice. Its rich texture and well-structured tannins lead to a long, memorable finish.

Hailing from Sonoma's Alexander Valley, this Cabernet Sauvignon is bold yet balanced. It showcases concentrated flavors of blackberry, black cherry, and cassis, with nuances of dark chocolate, cedar, and crushed herbs. The wine’s firm tannins and full body lead to a structured and persistent finish.

From the old vines of Lodi, this is a powerful and full-bodied Cabernet Sauvignon. It delivers an intense concentration of blackberry jam, dark chocolate, and licorice flavors, with strong notes of vanilla and toasted oak. Its immense structure and velvety tannins create a truly robust, "earth-shattering" finish.

This California Pinot Noir offers a smooth, accessible, and fruit-forward profile. It presents inviting aromas and flavors of ripe cherry, raspberry, and a hint of strawberry, complemented by subtle notes of vanilla and spice. With its soft tannins and silky texture, it is an easy-drinking, versatile wine.

products.fullName: The Four Graces Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: An elegant expression of Willamette Valley Pinot Noir, this wine is known for its complexity and grace. It reveals layers of red cherry, cranberry, and raspberry, interwoven with earthy notes of mushroom, baking spice, and a hint of rose petal. Fine-grained tannins and bright acidity create a long, refined finish.

From California's Central Coast, this Sauvignon Blanc is both aromatic and refreshing. It offers an appealing mix of citrus, like grapefruit and lime, along with riper tropical fruit notes of passion fruit and guava. A bright, zesty acidity provides a clean, crisp, and lively finish that is very versatile.

Breaking the rules of sparkling wine, this Cali Gold from 19 Crimes has a touch of sweetness to complement its vibrant fruit. It pops with flavors of ripe pear and pineapple, balanced by a crisp freshness. Gilded with a gold label, it's a defiant and celebratory choice for any occasion.

Hailing from the winery's Miller Ranch vineyard in Napa Valley, this Sauvignon Blanc is a vibrant and refreshing wine. It is fermented in stainless steel to preserve its fresh character, offering notes of grapefruit, lime, and melon with a crisp acidity and a clean, beautifully focused finish.

A quintessential expression of Oregon's renowned Pinot Noir, Firesteed is elegant and approachable. It presents a delicate bouquet of red cherry, raspberry, and cranberry, accented by subtle notes of earthy forest floor and spice. Its light body and silky tannins make it incredibly versatile.

An incredibly charming and aromatic Prosecco from Italy, perfect for any celebration or casual sip. It delights the senses with a fragrant bouquet of green apple, pear, and delicate acacia flowers. Its fine bubbles and fresh, fruity palate lead to a crisp, clean, and utterly enjoyable finish.

A classic Italian sparkling wine, Riondo Prosecco is light, crisp, and wonderfully refreshing. It offers an inviting nose of fresh green apple, pear, and bright citrus. The palate is lively and clean, with a gentle effervescence that makes it an exceptionally easy-drinking and versatile sparkler.

A vibrant and crisp sparkling wine from California, Banshee Brut is crafted for pure enjoyment. It offers a lively palate of green apple, tart pear, and a hint of citrus zest, all supported by fine, persistent bubbles. A touch of toast on the finish adds complexity to this refreshing sparkler.

Sourced from Washington's Columbia Valley, this Cabernet Sauvignon is known for its accessible, fruit-forward style. It offers plush flavors of black cherry, blackberry, and dark plum, complemented by subtle hints of coffee, spice, and vanilla from oak aging. Soft tannins contribute to a smooth, easy finish.

A classic expression of California Cabernet Sauvignon, this wine balances rich fruit with savory complexity. It displays notes of dark cherry, blackberry, and plum, layered with hints of roasted coffee, vanilla, and sweet herbs. Structured tannins provide a satisfying and well-rounded finish for the price point.

products.fullName: Our Daily Cab Cabernet Sauvignon 750 Ml
products.description: This Cabernet Sauvignon is crafted from organic grapes and contains no added sulfites, offering a pure expression of the varietal. It presents fresh, vibrant flavors of black cherry and ripe plum with subtle herbal undertones. Its soft texture and smooth finish make it an accessible, easy-drinking red wine.

From the warm Lodi appellation, this Cabernet Sauvignon is bold and fruit-forward. It delivers intense flavors of blackberry jam, dark cherry, and plum, with a distinct profile of cinnamon, vanilla, and toasted oak. Its full body and robust tannins lead to a powerful, lingering finish reflecting its region.

This Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon offers a modern, balanced style. It focuses on vibrant fruit character, showing notes of black cherry, raspberry, and plum, with subtle undertones of dark chocolate, cedar, and graphite. Well-integrated tannins and fresh acidity create a wine of finesse and drinkability.

This Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon, part of the Michael Mondavi Family Estate, offers classic character. It features a rich core of black cherry, cassis, and plum flavors, enhanced by notes of mocha, cedar, and a hint of black pepper. Supple tannins and balanced acidity create a smooth, elegant wine.

A benchmark for Washington State Chardonnay, this wine offers a harmonious balance of fruit and subtle oak. It presents notes of pear, apple, and a touch of tropical fruit, complemented by creamy hints of butter, vanilla, and toasted almond. Its bright acidity ensures a crisp, refreshing finish.

A classic California-style Chardonnay, this wine is known for its rich and creamy profile. It features ripe flavors of baked apple, pear, and tropical fruits, generously layered with notes of butterscotch, vanilla, and toasted oak. A smooth, rounded texture leads to a lingering, decadent finish.

True to its name, this California Chardonnay is crafted in a rich, creamy, and buttery style. It offers decadent flavors of baked apple, pineapple, and vanilla bean, complemented by notes of toasted hazelnut and butterscotch. A full-bodied palate and smooth, luscious texture define this popular wine.

The "Riverstone" Chardonnay from Arroyo Seco, Monterey, is known for its rich texture and complexity. It features ripe flavors of pear, apricot, and citrus, enhanced by malolactic fermentation notes of butter, cream, and vanilla. A hint of minerality and bright acidity provide a balanced finish.

From the Adelaida District of Paso Robles, this Chardonnay balances richness with mountain acidity. It showcases a complex bouquet of pineapple, green apple, and honeydew melon, with notes of vanilla bean, toasted almond, and a distinct flinty minerality. A full-bodied wine with a crisp, elegant finish.

products.fullName: King Estate Acrobat Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: This Oregon Pinot Noir is crafted in an accessible, fruit-forward style. It offers a bright bouquet of strawberry, red cherry, and raspberry, with subtle hints of spice and earth. Its smooth texture, balanced acidity, and gentle tannins make it an excellent introduction to the wines of the region.

products.fullName: A To Z Pinot Noir 750 Ml
products.description: A benchmark for Oregon Pinot Noir, this wine blends fruit from across the state for complexity and consistency. It delivers a beautiful array of red fruit aromas like cherry and raspberry, alongside floral and earthy notes. Its balanced acidity and supple tannins make it both food-friendly and approachable.

A multi-appellation California Pinot Noir, this wine offers a rich, bold, and fruit-forward experience. Sourced from Sonoma, Monterey, and Santa Barbara counties, it features deep flavors of black cherry, plum, and raspberry, with notes of vanilla, spice, and toast. A plush texture defines its full finish.

products.fullName: Chateau Ste Michelle Fume/Sauvignon Blanc 750 Ml
products.description: This Columbia Valley Sauvignon Blanc is crisp, aromatic, and refreshing. It presents vibrant citrus notes of grapefruit and lime, along with green melon and a distinctive herbal character of fresh-cut grass and lemongrass. Its bright acidity and clean, zesty finish make it an invigorating white wine.

Labeled as Sauvignon Blanc, this Sonoma County wine balances bright fruit with subtle richness. It offers zesty aromas of grapefruit, lime, and passion fruit, with underlying notes of melon and lemongrass. A portion aged in oak adds texture and complexity, leading to a crisp, yet rounded finish.

A classic expression of Marlborough, New Zealand, this Sauvignon Blanc is intensely aromatic and vibrant. It explodes with pungent notes of passion fruit, grapefruit, and gooseberry, alongside classic herbaceous undertones of fresh-cut grass. Its zesty acidity provides a crisp, mouthwatering finish.

This Sonoma County Sauvignon Blanc is crafted in a bright, energetic style. It showcases a vibrant aromatic profile of grapefruit, white peach, and passion fruit, with a subtle hint of fresh herbs and minerality. The palate is crisp and focused, driven by zesty acidity that leads to a clean, refreshing finish.
